  <p>After a thorough design process with
    <a href="https://www.lizsiskillustration.com/">scientific illustrator Liz Sisk</a>, we moved forward with a dark, almost forest-like aesthetic. Dark websites present their own challenges. It can be difficult to blend a color scheme on a dark background and keep text clear and readable. In this case the approach was necessary in order to highlight the
    <em>incredible</em>
    macro bug photography Royce provided. In the final design, we settled on a dark feel for shopping-related pages and a softer look for information-heavy areas of the site.</p>
</div>
